==English==

===Etymology===
Latin ''[[stare]]'', "to stand"

===Noun===
{{en-noun|statuses}}

#A person’s [[position]] or [[standing]] relative to that of others.
#[[Prestige]] or high standing.
#A [[situation]] or [[state of affairs]].
#The [[legal]] [[condition]] of a person or thing.

